# The public replay demo requires NO environment variables to run.
# It reads only local sanitized static JSON and never contacts the X API.

# The original private engine reads a bearer token from its own .env.
# It is listed here only to document the variable name. Do not place a real
# value here, and do not add it to the Vercel deployment.
#
# X_BEARER_TOKEN=
#
# Live X access is intentionally disabled in the public demo.
#
# Never use NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefixed credentials. A NEXT_PUBLIC_ variable is
# exposed to the browser and must never hold a secret.
